message: for those of you who've been using coffeescript for a while now, has it met expectations?
I'm wrapping up a small project written in CS, and while I like the syntax, I'm not totally sold on its advantages
understanding what js results from an expression (which you need to do) takes up a big chunk of mental space
really loving cs, especially all the syntactic support for common js idioms
i just compile the cs and look at the js
